Extension: Cross-version Extension for R5.EvidenceReport for use in FHIR R4

Official URL: http://hl7.org/fhir/5.0/StructureDefinition/extension-EvidenceReport Version: 0.0.1-ballot
Standards status: Trial-use Computable Name: ext_R5_EvidenceReport
This cross-version extension represents EvidenceReport from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/EvidenceReport 5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4.

Context of Use

    This extension may be used on the following element(s)

    • Element ID: Basic

Usage info

Usages:

  • This Extension is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
